com.inqwell.any

Interface OrderComparator

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparator
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AnyComparator

    public interface OrderComparator
extends Comparator
    Compare Orderable children so that they can be ordered according to arbitrary elements under each child node.

    In the Any framework there is a need for only one comparator implementation.

    Version:
    $Revision: 1.2 $
    Author:
    $Author: sanderst $
